******************************************* PROCESS*******************************************
1. Create Project Folder & VS Code Setup
# 1. Create folder
mkdir sales-ai-assistant
cd sales-ai-assistant

# 2. Open in VS Code
code .
2. Install Python Extensions in VS Code
Install Python extension by Microsoft

Install Python Docstring Generator
3. Create Virtual Environment
# Terminal in VS Code (Ctrl+`)
python -m venv venv

# Activate (Windows)
venv\Scripts\activate

# Activate (Mac/Linux)
source venv/bin/activate
4. Install FREE Dependencies
Create requirements.txt:
flask==2.3.3
flask-cors==4.0.0
SpeechRecognition==3.10.0
pyaudio==0.2.11
transformers==4.35.0
torch==2.1.0
sentence-transformers==2.2.2
numpy==1.24.3
pandas==2.0.3
openai==0.28.1
python-dotenv==1.0.0
requests==2.31.0

Install:
pip install -r requirements.txt
